WEBVTT

00:04:28.692 --> 00:04:31.182
ani antisemiti,

00:04:31.206 --> 00:04:32.464
ale revizionisti.

00:04:32.991 --> 00:04:35.206
Hovorili: „Sme revizionisti.

00:04:35.230 --> 00:04:37.913
A máme jedno poslanie:

00:04:37.937 --> 00:04:41.497
opraviť chyby v histórii.“

00:04:42.369 --> 00:04:47.779
Ale stačí načrieť centimeter pod povrch.

00:04:47.803 --> 00:04:49.710
A viete, čo tam nájdete?

00:04:49.734 --> 00:04:52.224
Rovnaké obdivovanie Hitlera,

00:04:52.248 --> 00:04:54.123
velebenie Tretej ríše,

00:04:54.147 --> 00:04:57.089
antisemitizmus, rasizmus, predsudky.

00:04:57.904 --> 00:04:59.840
To ma zaujalo.